ure the collaboration","AOB: Devon asked if the task assignment was meant to be done in the present call but zalfred addressed that we were on holiday for the previous weeks and assignees will continue work on january as agreed in our previous call","AOB: ECOSYSTEM Update Videos: Zalfred and Killy proposed creating the leftover ecosystem videos"]}],"tags":{"topicsCovered":"Video Edit, Q1 2025 goals, Ecosystem Update videos, Zealy, Town Hall Videos","emotions":"Friendly, speedy , Collaborative, Thoughtful"},"type":"Custom","noSummaryGiven":false,"canceledSummary":false}', false, '2025-01-10 00:00:00', '2025-01-10 00:00:00');

