ion program.","There was also a suggestion to use the free tool like udemy for this purpose as that could also be a way to reach a wider audience","Meeting ended with some decisions to be shifted to next call"]}],"tags":{"topicsCovered":"CCCP, Project Updates, Platforms"},"type":"custom","noSummaryGiven":false,"canceledSummary":false,"noSummaryGivenText":"No Summary Given","canceledSummaryText":"Meeting was cancelled"}', false, '2025-05-07 00:00:00', '2025-05-07 00:00:00');

