d might be best for certification program with its in-built integrations. it also has the same modular approach as from the previous certification round","Tevo mentioned that Andamio platform can also be used for this purpose though modular approach wont be there and need to be built"]}],"tags":{"topicsCovered":"Process improvement, lms, portfolios"},"type":"custom","noSummaryGiven":false,"canceledSummary":false,"noSummaryGivenText":"No Summary Given","canceledSummaryText":"Meeting was cancelled"}', false, '2025-04-30 00:00:00', '2025-04-30 00:00:00');

